sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant A as Auth Service
    participant DB as User DB
    participant T as 2FA Service
    participant S as Session

    U->>F: login
    F->>A: auth request
    A->>DB: verify credentials
    DB-->>A: OK
    A->>T: 2FA challenge
    T-->>A: sent
    A-->>F: request 2FA code
    U->>F: enter code
    F->>A: verify
    A->>T: validate
    T-->>A: OK
    A->>S: create session
    S-->>A: token
    A-->>F: success
    F-->>U: logged in